          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fairness in Forgiveness Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to include as a public service job for purposes of the public service loan forgiveness program a full-time job as an employee of a management and operating contractor of a national laboratory owned by the Department of Energy. </p> <p> This bill and its amendments take effect as if enacted on October 1, 2007.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
